:: In a Hurry Intro {"position":"950,300","size":"200,100"}
In a hurry? No problem. Here's the short version:

* Full-stack .NET developer, 3+ years professional experience
* Enterprise CRM, Azure, C#, JavaScript -- that's my main lane
* Freelance work across various JS frameworks on the side
* Previously bootcamp -> apprentice -> dev II

I'm not gonna lie though -- I really hope most people don't go this route. I hope they actually enjoy the experience and find it novel. But if you just want to know what I look like on a piece of paper instead of what I'm actually like, that's fine too. I completely understand.

Where do you want to go?

