:: About Intro {"position":"50,850","size":"200,100"}
So, high level? I'm a full-stack software engineer. Passionate about a lot of things -- and I have a lot of hobbies that are, honestly, pretty far from my chosen career sometimes.

I love 3D printing, which isn't too far from software engineering -- I like tinkering with things, that kind of makes sense. But gardening? I have a real passion for gardening and horticulture. I actually originally thought I might go into plant science, but it just didn't end up being the thing for me.

Other than that, I'm a happily married man. I'm a Christian -- I attend church regularly, and my faith is a very important part of who I am.

But what specifically would you like to know?

