:: Elevator Pitch {"position":"50,1100","size":"200,100"}
I'm a full-stack .NET developer who builds systems that real people rely on every day.

Most of my work lives in enterprise tools -- complex workflows, data-driven systems, and software that has to be reliable because businesses run on it. I work primarily in C#, ASP.NET, JavaScript, and Azure, with freelance work across various JS frameworks on the side.

I care about the people I build for, the team I build with, and writing code that the next person can actually read.

That's the short version anyway. What else would you like to know?

[photo: elevator_pitch]

