:: Family {"position":"50,2100","size":"200,100"}
Family is huge for me. I'm happily married to my wife Ruthie -- it's just the two of us for now, but we're hoping for our family to grow in the coming years.

I come from a pretty large family. My immediate family only has five members -- my mom, my dad, my siblings, and me. But the extended family, especially on my mom's side, has a lot of cousins and uncles. We have very big get-togethers.

And now with my wife Ruthie's family as well, holidays are usually very busy for me. Because I have a lot of people who I love to see and interact with.

My grandpa is a doctor, my dad was an aircraft mechanic. They've both been really great influences -- very supportive of all of my endeavors. My mom too. They all showed me the value of working with your hands and solving problems, which is kind of where all of this started.

[photo: family]

