:: Hobbies Gaming {"position":"200,1350","size":"200,100"}
So one of my big hobbies is gaming. I built my own PC -- I've kind of always been really inclined to build things, especially technological things.

At a very high level, the reason I enjoy gaming is because it's an extremely interactive form of content. Art, media, whatever you want to call it. Some games have even been described as interactable movies.

I'm drawn to games that feel like worlds, not just mechanics. My wife Ruthie and I have played through all of the Dark Pictures games together -- story-driven horror, couch co-op, making terrible decisions and blaming each other for them. That's our thing.

This experience, for example, has grown out of my love for gaming and the love for the interaction and choice you get to have. This way, it can feel a lot more like we're having a conversation and you can actually feel like you're asking me the questions you want answered.

As time goes on, I'll even update this site to be based more on the questions people actually want to ask.

[photo: hobbies_gaming]

