:: Career Goals {"position":"750,1350","size":"200,100"}
Career goals? Well, there are a few areas that really excite me.

Space exploration is a big one. Basically anything that's futuristic, you know? Electric vehicles seem to be a huge step forward for our society -- moving to a more reusable form of energy. Same with solar panels. I feel like it would just be better for everybody if we were able to harness the big nuclear power plant that's in the sky called the sun.

I feel like it was put there intentionally so that we could use it to fuel our lives and our daily activity.

All of those things are more futuristic concepts that are coming more and more into our lives and pushing us closer to a high-tech, sci-fi future. Which I love.

And like I said, I would love to get into the gaming industry if the opportunity ever presents itself. But at the end of the day, as long as I'm doing meaningful work that helps people and helps our society become better, I'm good.

