:: Enterprise Projects {"position":"900,1100","size":"200,100"}
A lot of my work has been in enterprise and internal systems -- the software that businesses actually run on.

Built and maintained CRM workflows used to manage thousands of customer interactions and transactions. Designed engagement forms, contact management systems, and reporting dashboards that internal teams depend on daily.

On the technical side: Azure Functions, .NET Minimal APIs, optimized EF Core queries, CI/CD pipelines, D365 integrations, Azure Application Insights monitoring -- most of it cloud-hosted infrastructure that has to stay up.

The common thread: software where the details matter, the rules matter, and users will absolutely find the one path no one accounted for. That's the job.

