:: Personality Intro {"position":"1600,850","size":"200,100"}
What kind of person am I? Hopefully through the experience you've had with this site so far, you've been able to tell that I'm a pretty thoughtful dude.

I really try to create things with the user in mind first. And that translates to my personality -- I really do care about people. It's one of the biggest things about me, I'd say. I think about others a lot and how experiences will translate to them.

Right now, while you're reading this, I'm thinking about how you, the user, are going to look at this and what you'll think of it. What I can say to kind of form the makings of a connection.

Obviously, sadly, you're not interacting with me directly, so it's a little bit one-sided at this point. But hopefully, by the time you get to the end of this, it will become a two-way conversation.

