:: Why This Format {"position":"1750,1100","size":"200,100"}
Why did I make my portfolio like this? I love gaming. I wanted to show anyone interested in learning more about me that I'm more than qualifications on a page.

There are so many people out there, so many developers, who just have a pretty static page with the basic information about who they are. It shows you that they can build a website. But it doesn't show you their creativity, their passion, and you don't really get to know them at all through their site.

I wanted to do something I've never seen before -- something personal. And here we are.

[[How do you solve problems?->Problem Solving]]
