:: Resume Ending {"position":"600,2350","size":"200,100"}
Wow, alright... not gonna lie, I really hope most people aren't just skipping straight to this.

I hope people actually enjoy the experience and find it novel. But if you didn't, and you just want to know what I look like on a piece of paper instead of what I'm actually like -- that's fine too. I completely understand.

Here is my resume, as requested. But before you go -- I built this whole experience to give dimension to the words on that two-dimensional page. To show you that I'm not just a list of bullet points, but a person.

I hope you enjoyed your visit. Please do reach out if you think I can help you with anything!

